msgstr "Se hai bisogno di ulteriore assistenza, visita il Centro Assistenza"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_acknowledgement/email/body.txt:10
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:16
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:17
msgid "If you need further help, please visit the Help Center:"
msgstr "Se hai bisogno di ulteriore assistenza, visita il Centro Assistenza:"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_acknowledgement/email/subject.txt:3
msgid "Your edX financial assistance request"
msgstr "La tua richiesta di assistenza finanziaria su edX"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:21
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:5
msgid ""
"Congratulations, your Financial Assistance application has been approved. "
"Please see your coupon code below."
msgstr ""
"Congratulazioni, la tua domanda per l'assistenza finanziaria è stata "
"approvata. Vedi il codice coupon qui sotto."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:29
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:7
#, python-format
msgid "%(coupon_code)s"
msgstr "%(coupon_code)s"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:37
#, python-format
msgid ""
"edX offers an %(percentage_off)s discount to students who qualify for "
"financial assistance. The deadline to apply this discount is"
msgstr ""
"edX offre uno sconto del %(percentage_off)s agli studenti che rientrano nei "
"requisiti per l'assistenza finanziaria. La scadenza per applicare questo "
"sconto è"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:41
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:9
#, python-format
msgid "%(coupon_expiry_date)s."
msgstr "%(coupon_expiry_date)s."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:45
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:11
msgid "To apply the discount, follow the steps below:"
msgstr "Per applicare lo sconto, segui i seguenti passaggi:"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:53
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:13
msgid "Visit the redeem discount page:"
msgstr "Visita la pagina per riscattare lo sconto:"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:59
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:15
msgid ""
"Click the \"Checkout\" button of the course for which you requested "
"financial assistance"
msgstr ""
"Clicca sul pulsante \"Checkout\" del corso per il quale hai richiesto "
"assistenza finanziaria"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:64
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:17
msgid ""
"Verify that the price of your course has been reduced, then enter your "
"payment information"
msgstr ""
"Verifica che il prezzo del tuo corso sia stato ridotto, quindi inserisci le "
"informazioni di pagamento"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:72
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:19
msgid "After that, you will be able to check out with the discount in place."
msgstr "Dopo di che, potrai procedere al pagamento con lo sconto applicato."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.html:80
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:21
msgid ""
"Thank you for your participation with edX. We hope you enjoy the course!"
msgstr ""
"Grazie per la tua partecipazione su edX. Speriamo che il corso ti piaccia!"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/body.txt:9
#, python-format
msgid ""
"edX offers an 80%% discount to students who qualify for financial "
"assistance. The deadline to apply this discount is"
msgstr ""
"edX offre uno sconto dell'80%% agli studenti che rientrano nei requisiti per"
" l'assistenza finanziaria. La scadenza per applicare questo sconto è"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_approved/email/subject.txt:3
msgid ""
"Congratulations! Your financial assistance application has been approved"
msgstr ""
"Congratulazioni! La tua domanda per l'assistenza finanziaria è stata "
"approvata"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:21
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:4
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in edX. We have reviewed your financial "
"assistance application, and unfortunately, it was not accepted."
msgstr ""
"Grazie per il tuo interesse in edX. Abbiamo esaminato la tua domanda per "
"l'assistenza finanziaria e, sfortunatamente, non è stata accettata."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:29
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:6
msgid ""
"We apologize, this course isn't eligible for financial assistance. We "
"encourage you to apply again for another edX course that isn't restricted."
msgstr ""
"Ci scusiamo, questo corso non è idoneo per l'assistenza finanziaria. Ti "
"invitiamo a fare un'altra richiesta per un corso edX che non sia soggetto a "
"restrizioni."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:36
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:8
msgid "You can view a list of restricted courses in our Help Center:"
msgstr ""
"Puoi visualizzare l'elenco dei corsi soggetti a restrizioni nel nostro "
"Centro Assistenza:"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.html:43
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:10
msgid "We encourage you to keep exploring:"
msgstr "Ti invitiamo a continuare a esplorare:"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/body.txt:4
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in edX. We have reviewed your financial "
"assistance application, and it was not accepted."
msgstr ""
"Grazie per il tuo interesse in edX. Abbiamo esaminato la tua domanda per "
"l'assistenza finanziaria e non è stata accettata."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_course_restriction/email/subject.txt:3
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/subject.txt:3
msgid "Update regarding your financial assistance application"
msgstr "Aggiornamento sulla tua domanda per l'assistenza finanziaria"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:13
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:2
#, python-format
msgid "Hello %(user_name)s,"
msgstr "Caro %(user_name)s,"

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:21
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in edX. We have reviewed your financial "
"assistance application, and unfortunately, it was not accepted. "
msgstr ""
"Grazie per il tuo interesse in edX. Abbiamo esaminato la tua domanda per "
"l'assistenza finanziaria e, sfortunatamente, non è stata accettata. "

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:27
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:6
msgid ""
"Financial assistance is limited and may only be awarded up to five times, "
"and you've reached the limit of five."
msgstr ""
"L'assistenza finanziaria è limitata e può essere concessa al massimo cinque "
"volte, e hai raggiunto il limite di cinque."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:35
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:8
msgid "You are more than welcome to continue auditing the course."
msgstr ""
"Sei più che benvenuto a continuare a seguire il corso in modalità audit."

#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.html:43
#: templates/financial_assistance/edx_ace/application_denied_limit/email/body.txt:10
msgid "Please let us know if you have any additional questions."
msgstr "Facci sapere se hai ulteriori domande."
